---
import AppLayout from '../layouts/AppLayout.astro';
---

<AppLayout
  title="Coming Soon"
  description="This feature is coming soon to VibeCodingWiki"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    <article class="rounded border border-[#a2a9b1] bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">
      <h1 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-semibold text-[#202122]">Coming Soon</h1>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-[#202122]">
        <p class="text-lg">
          This feature is currently under development and will be available soon.
        </p>

        <p>
          VibeCodingWiki is actively being developed with new features and improvements being added regularly.
          Stay tuned for updates!
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 rounded border border-[#c8ccd1] bg-[#f8f9fa] p-4">
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-[#202122]">What to do in the meantime?</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-[#54595d]">
            <li>Browse existing <a href="/wiki" class="text-[#0645ad] hover:text-[#0b0080]">wiki articles</a></li>
            <li>Check out the <a href="/roadmap" class="text-[#0645ad] hover:text-[#0b0080]">roadmap</a> to see what's planned</li>
            <li>View <a href="/users" class="text-[#0645ad] hover:text-[#0b0080]">contributors</a> who are building VibeCodingWiki</li>
            <li>Subscribe to the <a href="/newsletter" class="text-[#0645ad] hover:text-[#0b0080]">newsletter</a> for updates</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</AppLayout>
